snippet: Five football players were charged Tuesday with raping a fellow student near their high school in Winter Springs, and investigators say the student captured part of the attack on video.
abstract: Five football players from Winter Springs High School in Florida are charged with gang rape of fellow student in woods near school grounds; investigators say victim caught part of attack on video.
lead_paragraph: Five football players were charged Tuesday with raping a fellow student near their high school in Winter Springs, and investigators say the student captured part of the attack on video.

headline.main: Florida: 5 High School Students Are Accused of Gang Rape
